query:
SELECT ul.playerName, ul.upgradeType, ul.badgeOrAttribute, ul.fromValue, ul.toValue, p.name as matchedPlayer, p.team 
FROM upgrade_log ul 
LEFT JOIN players p ON ul.playerName = p.name 
LEFT JOIN player_aliases pa ON ul.playerName = pa.alias 
LEFT JOIN players p2 ON pa.playerId = p2.id 
WHERE ul.playerName IN ('De''Aaron Fox', 'Egor Demin', 'Kristaps Porzingis', 'Berringer') 
ORDER BY ul.playerName
